events.1883: Town occupied by French forces under command of Gustave Borgnis-Desbordes.
events.1920: Bamako becomes capital of colonial French Sudan.
events.1929: Submersible causeway to Sotuba built across the Niger River.
events.1960: City becomes capital of the Republic of Mali.
events.1975: Twin city relationship established with Angers, France.
events.1980: Saharan states summit held in city.
events.1991: Anti-government protest; crackdown. Malian coup d'état occurs.
events.2002: African Cup of Nations football contest held in Bamako.
events.2015: 2015 Bamako hotel attack occurs in Hippodrome.
events.2016: Attack on headquarters of the European Union military training mission in Bamako.
